Golden Empire Youth Tackle Football & Cheer
data.meta_description: Golden Empire Youth Tackle Football and Cheer is Kern County’s largest high school feeder program. It was developed for the purpose of providing a competitive football program that would not only encourage outstanding athletic performance, sportsmanship and team play, but also give participants an opportunity to play on teams with players in their high school district with whom they will continue playing with in high school.
